data.description:
Motivated seller considering ALL offers! With one of the largest floorplans in the community, this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home has room for it all! This home's major components are all relatively NEW!! Your peace of mind is assured with a brand new roof installed in 2020.The HVAC system is newly replaced at 2019. Windows redone in 2013 maximize energy efficiency and natural light. New wood flooring done in 2019 adds timeless elegance and effortless maintenance. Experience a fresh start with all-new interior and exterior paint including the driveway creating a crisp and inviting ambiance throughout the home. Updated ceiling fans enhance air circulation, contributing to your ultimate comfort. The property boasts a meticulously landscaped yard with mature citrus trees, providing an enchanting outdoor retreat. The lanai is your private oasis, featuring a new exterior storm door for a seamless indoor-outdoor experience. The owner has taken meticulous care of this home. 
This home is located in a thriving 55+ community renowned for its wealth of amenities and activities. From social gatherings in the clubhouse or healthy habits in the fitness center, you'll find endless opportunities to stay engaged and fulfilled. Embrace the exceptional comforts of modern living within a community that caters to your active lifestyle. This property offers more than just a home; it offers a vibrant, enriching way of life.
Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable house your home within this dynamic 55+ community. Schedule a viewing today and embark on a new chapter filled with exciting adventures and lasting memories!
